plot: The day trip to Beverly Hills continues and Shannon surprises the group with tourist clothes and a double decker bus ride through Hollywood. Tamra confronts Braunwyn about going behind her back and secretly communicating with her enemies. Emily leaves the trip early to see Shane after he returns from taking the Bar exam and becomes disappointed when he is less than enthusiastic about reuniting. Braunwyn has dinner with her mom Dr. Deb and admits to lying to her new friends but places the blame on her unconventional childhood. Tamra and Shannon learn more about Braunwyn when they take a hip-hop dance class. Gina misses a court appearance and a warrant is issued for her arrest.
